`ctrl` 이 움직이는 키

## Focus
meta+c: center
meta+shift+c: focus mode change

## Window manipulating
meta+n: new window

## Move Window
meta+i: move nest window to sibling
meta+o: out
meta+shift+o: out other
meta+t: move window

## Resize window
meta+f: full
meta+r: resize

## Scroll (`,`/`.` `arrow`)
* meta + ,/. : focus next/previous
* meta + `[`/`]`: scroll
* meta + arrow: focus next/previous
* meta + home/end: focus home/end

## Workspace (PgUp/PgDn)
* `super` + `PgUp/PgDn`: witch workspace

## Scratch (`super+escape`)
* `super-scape`: toggle scratch window
* `super+escape` + `ctrl` : move current window to scratch
<!-- * `super+escape` + `shift`: toggle-floating scratch layer -->

## Monitor (`sufer+shift`)
* `super+shift` + `r/l arrow`
* `super+shift` + `ctrl` + `r/l arrow`
